  06 Apr 2015; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> libixion-0.9.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Rekeyword, add subslot, disable python-3 for now, bug 545562

*libixion-0.9.0 (05 Apr 2015)

  05 Apr 2015; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  -libixion-0.5.0.ebuild, +libixion-0.9.0.ebuild, libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Version bump; remove old

  04 Apr 2015; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild,
  libixion-0.7.0.ebuild, libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Package moved to gitlab, bug 544834

  15 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libixion-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #534684

  15 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libixion-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #534684

  08 Feb 2015; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild,
  libixion-0.7.0.ebuild, libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Update live ebuild and improve dependencies, thanks to Andreas Sturmlechner

  28 Dec 2014; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Minor updates to ebuild

  14 Sep 2014; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> libixion-0.7.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Restore keywords on 0.7 for upcoming LO-4.3 bump; drop subslot

  26 May 2014; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> libixion-0.7.0.ebuild:
  Drop keywords of 0.7.0 temporarily since it is only needed by libreoffice live
  ebuild

  27 Mar 2014; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> libixion-0.7.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Raise dep over mdds to > 0.10. Fixes bug#505898

*libixion-0.7.0 (25 Mar 2014)

  25 Mar 2014; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> +libixion-0.7.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Version bump to 0.7 series needed by git libreoffice.

  27 Oct 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #486204

  20 Oct 2013; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Marked stable on AMD64 based on arch testing by Elijah "Armageddon" El
  Lazkani in bug #486204.

  10 Jul 2013; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Subslot the ixion dep too.

  10 Jul 2013; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Boost is actually linked to ixion so depend on it properly.

  19 Apr 2013; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> libixion-0.5.0.ebuild,
  libixion-9999.ebuild:
  Keyword ~arm.

